Great question Lets go through your list carefully and identify which points connect with the topics recurring issues and urgency of student voices. --- Recurring Issues These are problems that keep happening repeatedly and affect daily student life:
  1. Mess food (sambar) Constant complaints about taste and quality.
  1. Mosquitoes Happens regularly due to lack of maintenance.
  1. Hot water Frequent unavailability, especially during mornings.
  1. Network issues Common problem affecting online work and communication.
  1. Cleaning Repeated neglect of hostel or classroom hygiene.
  1. Teaching method & staff Ongoing dissatisfaction about teaching style or approach.
  1. Placement & training issues Continual concern about lack of opportunities
